      • getPublications

        List<StandardDocument.Standard.Publication> getPublications()
        Returns the access to the fields belonging to the publications fields in this document.

        The returned list does not support the set method and its remove method always return null, even when it removes a value.

        Returns:
        the access to the fields belonging to the publications fields in this document.

        8.1.0
